S.FORM: Albert II I 1958 a miheca saka 3 folad saka 14 a romi'ad masofoc ci Albert II, malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Monaco anini i ci Albert II, patirengan a romi'ad i 2005 a miheca saka 4 folad saka 6 a romi'ad. Kasofocan a loma' 出生家庭 lalamod 配偶 salikaka 兄弟姐妹 natayalan 事蹟 pitooran 宗教
